2231 /*
2232 * <format id> ::= <expression> |
2233 */
2234 case FORMAT_ID1:
2235 nondevice_io = TRUE;
2236 chk_fmtid(RHS(1));
2237 break;
2238 /*
2239 * <format id> ::= *
2240 */
2241 case FORMAT_ID2:
2242 chk_fmtid((SST *)NULL);
2243 break;
2244
2245 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2246 /*
2247 * <fid or nid> ::= <expression> |
2248 */
2249 case FID_OR_NID1:
2250 if (!XBIT(137, 0x010000))
2251 nondevice_io = TRUE;
2252 if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_IDENT) {
2253 sptr = refsym(SST_SYMG(RHS(1)), OC_OTHER);
2254 if (STYPEG(sptr) == ST_NML)
2255 goto nml_io;
2256 }
2257 chk_fmtid(RHS(1));
2258 break;
2259 /*
2260 * <fid or nid> ::= *
2261 */
2262 case FID_OR_NID2:
2263 chk_fmtid((SST *)NULL);
2264 unit_star = TRUE;
2265 break;
2266
2267 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2268 /*
2269 * <print spec> ::= <fid or nid>
2270 */
2271 case PRINT_SPEC1:
2272 chk_unitid((SST *)NULL);
2273 noparens = TRUE;
2274 if (unit_star)
2275 print_star = TRUE;
2276 goto io_init;
2277
2278 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2279 /*
2280 * <io spec> ::= <iolp> <spec list> ) <optional comma> |
2281 */
2282 case IO_SPEC1:
2283 goto io_init;
2284
2285 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2286 /*
2287 * <read spec2> ::= <iolp> <spec list> ) |
2288 */
2289 case READ_SPEC21:
2290 goto io_init;
2291 /*
2292 * <read spec2> ::= <fid or nid> |
2293 */
2294 case READ_SPEC22:
2295 /* fall thru */
2296
2297 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2298 /*
2299 * <read spec3> ::= <format id>
2300 */
2301 case READ_SPEC31:
2302 /* fall thru */
2303
2304 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2305 /*
2306 * <read spec4> ::= <fid or nid>
2307 */
2308 case READ_SPEC41:
2309 chk_unitid((SST *)NULL);
2310 noparens = TRUE;
2311
2312 io_init:
2313 if (PTS(PT_POS) && PTS(PT_REC)) {
2314 IOERR2(201, "Both POS and REC cannot be specified");
2315 }
2316 UNIT_CHECK;
2317 PT_CHECK(PT_REC, astb.ptr0);
2318
2319 if (PTV(PT_POS)) {
2320 ast = PTV(PT_POS);
2321 if (A_DTYPEG(ast) != DT_INT8)
2322 ast = mk_convert(ast, DT_INT8);
2323 ast1 = mk_unop(OP_VAL, astb.i1, DT_INT4);
2324 ast2 = mk_unop(OP_VAL, ast, DT_INT8);
2325 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_aux_init, DT_INT, 0);
2326 (void)begin_io_call(A_CALL, sptr, 2);
2327 (void)add_io_arg(ast1);
2328 (void)add_io_arg(ast2);
2329 (void)add_stmt_after(io_call.ast, (int)STD_PREV(0));
2330 }
2331 iomsg_check();
2332 if (fmttyp == FT_UNFORMATTED) {
2333 if (intern)
2334 IOERR(211);
2335 if (PTV(PT_ASYNCHRONOUS) || PTV(PT_ID)) {
2336 PT_CHECK(PT_ASYNCHRONOUS, astb.ptr0c);
2337 PT_CHECK(PT_ID, astb.ptr0);
2338 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_unf_asynca, DT_INT, 0);
2339 (void)begin_io_call(A_CALL, sptr, 2);
2340 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ASYNCHRONOUS));
2341 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ID));
2342 (void)add_stmt_after(io_call.ast, (int)STD_PREV(0));
2343 }
2344 sptr = mk_iofunc(unf_nm[LARGE_ARRAY_IDX][BYTE_SWAPPED_IO_IDX].init,
2345 DT_INT, 0);
2346 fix_iostat();
2347 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 5);
2348 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(is_read, DT_INT));
2349 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2350 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_REC));
2351 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2352 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2353 ast = end_io_call();
2354 if (rw03) {
2355 if (PTV(PT_BLANK))
2356 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_BLANK));
2357 if (PTV(PT_DECIMAL))
2358 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_DECIMAL));
2359 if (PTV(PT_DELIM))
2360 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_DELIM));
2361 if (PTV(PT_PAD))
2362 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_PAD));
2363 if (PTV(PT_ROUND))
2364 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_ROUND));
2365 if (PTV(PT_SIGN))
2366 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_SIGN));
2367 }
2368 } else { /* FORMATTED I/O */
2369 if (fmttyp == FT_LIST_DIRECTED)
2370 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.ptr0;
2371 else if (fmttyp == FT_NML)
2372 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.ptr0;
2373 else if (fmttyp == FT_FMTSTR) {
2374 /*
2375 * a character variable be initialized with the character
2376 * constant construct from the edit list in the FORMAT
2377 * statement. Can't treat this the same as FT_CHARACTER
2378 * because we may not know the actual length at the time
2379 * of the read/write statement.
2380 * Just issue a call to the encode routine which expects a
2381 * a character variable and record the fact that it was called.
2382 */
2383 if (fmt_is_var) {
2384 /*
2385 * integer variable containing the address of a character
2386 * string.
2387 */
2388 fmt_is_var = 0;
2389 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_encode_fmtv, DT_INT, 0);
2390 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 1);
2391 } else {
2392 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_encode_fmta, DT_INT, 0);
2393 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 3);
2394 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval((INT)ty_to_lib[TY_CHAR], DT_INT));
2395 (void)add_io_arg(astb.i1);
2396 }
2397 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_FMT));
2398 ast = end_io_call();
2399 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.ptr0;
2400 fmttyp = FT_CHARACTER; /* FMTSTR is now the same as character*/
2401 } else if (fmttyp != FT_ENCODED) {
2402 /*
2403 * if an unencoded format string is to be used in this
2404 * statement, first issue a call to the encode routine
2405 * and record the fact that it was called.
2406 */
2407 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_encode_fmta, DT_INT, 0);
2408 ast = PTV(PT_FMT);
2409 ast1 = mk_cval((INT)ty_to_lib[DTYG(A_DTYPEG(ast))], DT_INT);
2410 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 3);
2411 (void)add_io_arg(ast1); /* kind of format string */
2412 if (fmt_length)
2413 (void)add_io_arg(fmt_length); /* number of elements */
2414 else
2415 /*
2416 * if fmt_length is zero, then the unencoded format
2417 * character string is just a scalar, constant, subscripted
2418 * reference, or substring reference. Use the calling
2419 * convention to pass its length.
2420 */
2421 (void)add_io_arg(astb.i1);
2422 (void)add_io_arg(ast); /* format string */
2423 ast = end_io_call();
2424 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.ptr0;
2425 }
2426 if (intern) { /* INTERNAL I/O */
2427 /*
2428 * construct AST's to represent the number of array
2429 * elements of the character array or variable specified
2430 * as the unit id and the size of each record.
2431 */
2432 LOGICAL is_array;
2433 LOGICAL noncontig; /* non-contiguous array */
2434 int asd, i, ndim;
2435
2436 noncontig = FALSE;
2437 ast = ast3 = PTV(PT_UNIT);
2438 if (DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast)) != TY_ARRAY)
2439 is_array = FALSE;
2440 else
2441 is_array = TRUE;
2442 again:
2443 switch (A_TYPEG(ast)) {
2444 case A_ID:
2445 sptr = A_SPTRG(ast);
2446 goto do_intern;
2447 case A_MEM:
2448 sptr = A_SPTRG(A_MEMG(ast));
2449 if (is_array && DTY(DTYPEG(sptr)) != TY_ARRAY) {
2450 noncontig = TRUE;
2451 break;
2452 }
2453 do_intern: /* 'ast' is a scalar or whole array */
2454 if (DTY(DTYPEG(sptr)) != TY_ARRAY) /* a scalar */
2455 ast2 = astb.i1;
2456 else if (ASUMSZG(sptr))
2457 ast2 = astb.i0;
2458 else if (POINTERG(sptr)) {
2459 /* A possible section. Copy it to a contiguous
2460 * temporary.
2461 */
2462 noncontig = TRUE;
2463 } else {
2464 ast2 = AD_NUMELM(AD_PTR(sptr));
2465 }
2466 break;
2467
2468 case A_SUBSCR:
2469 /* assume an array element (or an irregular section,
2470 * which is an error)
2471 */
2472 ast2 = astb.i1;
2473 asd = A_ASDG(ast);
2474 ndim = ASD_NDIM(asd);
2475 for (i = 0; i < ndim; ++i) {
2476 int ss = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
2477
2478 if (A_TYPEG(ss) == A_TRIPLE)
2479 noncontig = TRUE;
2480 else if (A_SHAPEG(ss)) {
2481 /* a vector subscript -- illegal! */
2482 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
2483 "An internal file cannot be a character "
2484 "array with a vector subscript",
2485 "");
2486 noncontig = FALSE;
2487 is_array = FALSE;
2488 break;
2489 }
2490 }
2491 if (noncontig)
2492 break;
2493 noncontig = is_array;
2494 break;
2495
2496 case A_SUBSTR:
2497 ast = A_LOPG(ast); /* the 'parent' char scalar or
2498 * array section variable. 'ast3'
2499 * stores the A_SUBSTR AST. */
2500 if (is_array) {
2501 noncontig = TRUE;
2502 break;
2503 }
2504 goto again;
2505
2506 default:
2507 interr("semantio-int.io, bad ast", ast, 3);
2508 }
2509 if (noncontig) {
2510 /* A noncontiguous array:
2511 * + array section
2512 * + array substring
2513 * + array%member
2514 * + array%member(subscript)
2515 * + ...
2516 * Copy it to a contiguous temporary.
2517 */
2518 intern_array = ast3;
2519 intern_tmp = copy_replic_sect_to_tmp(intern_array);
2520 PTV(PT_UNIT) = intern_tmp;
2521 ast2 = AD_NUMELM(AD_PTR(A_SPTRG(intern_tmp)));
2522 }
2523 /*
2524 * since the UNIT is character, its length is passed as
2525 * the last argument. We rely on the passing mechanism
2526 * to effect this. IF we have a situation where this
2527 * isn't true, we'll need to make this section conditional
2528 * on the target.
2529 */
2530 fix_iostat();
2531 if (fmttyp == FT_LIST_DIRECTED) {
2532 if (is_read)
2533 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldr_intern_inita;
2534 else
2535 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldw_intern_inita;
2536 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2537
2538 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2539 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2540 (void)add_io_arg(ast2);
2541 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2542 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2543 ast = end_io_call();
2544 } else if (fmttyp == FT_NML) { /* Namelist I/O */
2545 if (is_read)
2546 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_nmlr_intern_inita;
2547 else
2548 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_nmlw_intern_inita;
2549 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2550
2551 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2552 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2553 (void)add_io_arg(ast2);
2554 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2555 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2556 ast = end_io_call();
2557 } else {
2558 if (is_read)
2559 rtlRtn = fmt_init[1].read[fmt_is_var];
2560 else
2561 rtlRtn = fmt_init[1].write[fmt_is_var];
2562 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2563 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 5);
2564 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2565 (void)add_io_arg(ast2);
2566 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2567 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2568 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_FMT));
2569 ast = end_io_call();
2570 }
2571 } else { /* EXTERNAL I/O */
2572 fix_iostat();
2573 if (fmttyp == FT_LIST_DIRECTED) {
2574 if (is_read)
2575 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldr_init;
2576 else if (!print_star)
2577 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldw_init;
2578 else
2579 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_print_init;
2580 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2581 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2582 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2583 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_REC));
2584 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2585 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2586 ast = end_io_call();
2587 } else if (fmttyp == FT_NML) {
2588 if (is_read)
2589 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_nmlr_init;
2590 else
2591 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_nmlw_init;
2592 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2593 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2594 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2595 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_REC));
2596 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2597 if (bitv & BITV_IOSTAT)
2598 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2599 else
2600 (void)add_io_arg(mk_fake_iostat());
2601 ast = end_io_call();
2602 } else {
2603 if (is_read) {
2604 rtlRtn = fmt_init[0].read[fmt_is_var];
2605 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2606 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 7);
2607 } else {
2608 rtlRtn = fmt_init[0].write[fmt_is_var];
2609 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2610 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 6);
2611 }
2612 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_UNIT));
2613 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_REC));
2614 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2615 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2616 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_FMT));
2617 if (is_read) {
2618 PT_CHECK(PT_SIZE, astb.ptr0);
2619 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_SIZE));
2620 }
2621 PT_CHECK(PT_ADVANCE, astb.ptr0c);
2622 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ADVANCE));
2623 ast = end_io_call();
2624 }
2625 }
2626 if (rw03) {
2627 if (is_read) {
2628 if (PTV(PT_DELIM))
2629 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_DELIM));
2630 if (PTV(PT_SIGN))
2631 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_SIGN));
2632 } else {
2633 if (PTV(PT_BLANK))
2634 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_BLANK));
2635 if (PTV(PT_PAD))
2636 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_PAD));
2637 }
2638 if (fmttyp == FT_LIST_DIRECTED) {
2639 if (is_read) {
2640 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldr_init03a;
2641 PT_CHECK(PT_BLANK, astb.ptr0c);
2642 PT_CHECK(PT_DECIMAL, astb.ptr0c);
2643 PT_CHECK(PT_PAD, astb.ptr0c);
2644 PT_CHECK(PT_ROUND, astb.ptr0c);
2645 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2646 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 5);
2647 (void)add_io_arg(A_DESTG(ast));
2648 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_BLANK));
2649 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DECIMAL));
2650 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_PAD));
2651 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ROUND));
2652 } else {
2653 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldw_init03a;
2654 if (PTV(PT_ROUND))
2655 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_ROUND));
2656 PT_CHECK(PT_DECIMAL, astb.ptr0c);
2657 PT_CHECK(PT_DELIM, astb.ptr0c);
2658 PT_CHECK(PT_SIGN, astb.ptr0c);
2659 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2660 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2661 (void)add_io_arg(A_DESTG(ast));
2662 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DECIMAL));
2663 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DELIM));
2664 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_SIGN));
2665 }
2666 ast = end_io_call();
2667 } else if (fmttyp == FT_NML) {
2668 if (is_read) {
2669 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_nmlr_init03a;
2670 PT_CHECK(PT_BLANK, astb.ptr0c);
2671 PT_CHECK(PT_DECIMAL, astb.ptr0c);
2672 PT_CHECK(PT_PAD, astb.ptr0c);
2673 PT_CHECK(PT_ROUND, astb.ptr0c);
2674 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2675 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 5);
2676 (void)add_io_arg(A_DESTG(ast));
2677 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_BLANK));
2678 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DECIMAL));
2679 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_PAD));
2680 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ROUND));
2681 } else {
2682 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_nmlw_init03a;
2683 if (PTV(PT_ROUND))
2684 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_ROUND));
2685 PT_CHECK(PT_DECIMAL, astb.ptr0c);
2686 PT_CHECK(PT_DELIM, astb.ptr0c);
2687 PT_CHECK(PT_SIGN, astb.ptr0c);
2688 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2689 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2690 (void)add_io_arg(A_DESTG(ast));
2691 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DECIMAL));
2692 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DELIM));
2693 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_SIGN));
2694 }
2695 ast = end_io_call();
2696 } else {
2697 if (is_read) {
2698 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_fmtr_init03a;
2699 PT_CHECK(PT_BLANK, astb.ptr0c);
2700 PT_CHECK(PT_DECIMAL, astb.ptr0c);
2701 PT_CHECK(PT_PAD, astb.ptr0c);
2702 PT_CHECK(PT_ROUND, astb.ptr0c);
2703 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2704 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 5);
2705 (void)add_io_arg(A_DESTG(ast));
2706 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_BLANK));
2707 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DECIMAL));
2708 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_PAD));
2709 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ROUND));
2710 } else {
2711 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_fmtw_init03a;
2712 if (PTV(PT_DELIM))
2713 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(PT_DELIM));
2714 PT_CHECK(PT_DECIMAL, astb.ptr0c);
2715 PT_CHECK(PT_SIGN, astb.ptr0c);
2716 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2717 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 4);
2718 (void)add_io_arg(A_DESTG(ast));
2719 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_DECIMAL));
2720 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_SIGN));
2721 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_ROUND));
2722 }
2723 ast = end_io_call();
2724 }
2725 /*
2726 * ast is an A_ASN of the form
2727 * z_io = ..._init03(...)
2728 */
2729 }
2730 }
2731 ast = add_cgoto(ast);
2732 break;
2733
2734 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2735 /*
2736 * <encode spec> ::= <iolp> <encode unit> <encode ctl> )
2737 */
2738 case ENCODE_SPEC1:
2739 if (flg.standard)
2740 error(171, 2, gbl.lineno, "ENCODE/DECODE", CNULL);
2741 if (fmttyp == FT_FMTSTR) {
2742 /*
2743 * a character variable be initialized with the character
2744 * constant construct from the edit list in the FORMAT
2745 * statement. Can't treat this the same as FT_CHARACTER
2746 * because we may not know the actual length at the time
2747 * of the read/write statement.
2748 * Just issue a call to the encode routine which expects a
2749 * a character variable and record the fact that it was called.
2750 */
2751 if (fmt_is_var) {
2752 /*
2753 * integer variable contiaining address of a character
2754 * string.
2755 */
2756 fmt_is_var = 0;
2757 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_encode_fmtv, DT_INT, 0);
2758 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 1);
2759 } else {
2760 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_encode_fmta, DT_INT, 0);
2761 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 3);
2762 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval((INT)ty_to_lib[TY_CHAR], DT_INT));
2763 (void)add_io_arg(astb.i1);
2764 }
2765 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_FMT));
2766 ast = end_io_call();
2767 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.ptr0;
2768 fmttyp = FT_CHARACTER; /* FMTSTR is now the same as character*/
2769 } else if (fmttyp != FT_ENCODED) {
2770 /*
2771 * if an unencoded format string is to be used in this
2772 * statement, first issue a call to the encode routine
2773 * and record the fact that it was called.
2774 */
2775 sptr = mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_encode_fmta, DT_INT, 0);
2776 ast = PTV(PT_FMT);
2777 ast1 = mk_cval((INT)ty_to_lib[DTYG(A_DTYPEG(ast))], DT_INT);
2778 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 3);
2779 (void)add_io_arg(ast1); /* kind of format string */
2780 if (fmt_length)
2781 (void)add_io_arg(fmt_length); /* number of elements */
2782 else
2783 (void)add_io_arg(astb.i1);
2784 (void)add_io_arg(ast); /* format string */
2785 ast = end_io_call();
2786 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.ptr0;
2787 }
2788 ast1 = mk_cval(is_read, DT_INT); /* read flag */
2789 ast2 = astb.i1; /* # of records is always 1 */
2790 fix_iostat();
2791 /*
2792 * decode-/encode- specific init routines are called.
2793 * Need to pass the 'loc' of the buffer to avoid passing
2794 * the length of the buffer if character; this also implies
2795 * the corresponding argument of the called function will be
2796 * a '**'. The actual length of the buffer is passed as an
2797 * explicit argument.
2798 */
2799 (void)sym_mkfunc_nodesc(mkRteRtnNm(RTE_loc), DT_ADDR);
2800 SST_UNITP(RHS(2), mk_unop(OP_LOC, SST_UNITG(RHS(2)), DT_PTR));
2801 if (fmttyp == FT_LIST_DIRECTED) {
2802 if (is_read)
2803 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldr_intern_inite;
2804 else
2805 rtlRtn = RTE_f90io_ldw_intern_inite;
2806 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2807 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 5);
2808 (void)add_io_arg((int)SST_UNITG(RHS(2)));
2809 (void)add_io_arg(ast2);
2810 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2811 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2812 (void)add_io_arg((int)SST_LENG(RHS(2)));
2813 } else {
2814 if (is_read)
2815 rtlRtn = fmt_inite.read[fmt_is_var];
2816 else
2817 rtlRtn = fmt_inite.write[fmt_is_var];
2818 sptr = mk_iofunc(rtlRtn, DT_INT, 0);
2819 (void)begin_io_call(A_FUNC, sptr, 6);
2820 (void)add_io_arg((int)SST_UNITG(RHS(2)));
2821 (void)add_io_arg(ast2);
2822 (void)add_io_arg(mk_cval(bitv, DT_INT));
2823 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_IOSTAT));
2824 (void)add_io_arg(PTARG(PT_FMT));
2825 (void)add_io_arg((int)SST_LENG(RHS(2)));
2826 }
2827 ast = end_io_call();
2828 ast = add_cgoto(ast);
2829 break;
2830
2831 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2832 /*
2833 * <encode unit> ::= <expression> , <format id> , <var ref>
2834 */
2835 case ENCODE_UNIT1:
2836 if (is_varref(RHS(5))) {
2837 (void)mkarg(RHS(5), &dum);
2838 ast1 = SST_ASTG(RHS(5));
2839 } else {
2840 IOERR(217);
2841 ast1 = astb.i0;
2842 }
2843 (void)chk_scalartyp(RHS(1), DT_INT, FALSE);
2844 SST_LENP(LHS, SST_ASTG(RHS(1)));
2845 SST_UNITP(LHS, ast1);
2846 break;
2847
2848 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2849 /*
2850 * <encode ctl> ::= |
2851 */
2852 case ENCODE_CTL1:
2853 break;
2854 /*
2855 * <encode ctl> ::= , <spec list>
2856 */
2857 case ENCODE_CTL2:
2858 break;
2859
2860 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2861 /*
2862 * <output list> ::= <output list> , <output item> |
2863 */
2864 case OUTPUT_LIST1:
2865 ((IOL *)SST_ENDG(RHS(1)))->next = (IOL *)SST_BEGG(RHS(3));
2866 SST_ENDP(RHS(1), SST_ENDG(RHS(3)));
2867 break;
2868 /*
2869 * <output list> ::= <elp> <output list> , <output item> ) |
2870 */
2871 case OUTPUT_LIST2:
2872 ((IOL *)SST_ENDG(RHS(2)))->next = (IOL *)SST_BEGG(RHS(4));
2873 SST_ENDP(RHS(2), SST_ENDG(RHS(4)));
2874 *LHS = *RHS(2);
2875 break;
2876 /*
2877 * <output list> ::= <output item>
2878 */
2879 case OUTPUT_LIST3:
2880 sem.defined_io_seen = 0;
2881 break;
2882
2883 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2884 /*
2885 * <output item> ::= <expression> |
2886 */
2887 case OUTPUT_ITEM1:
2888 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1));
2889 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
2890 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
2891 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_DERIVED && UNLPOLYG(DTY(dtype + 3))) {
2892 error(155, 4, gbl.lineno,
2893 "Unlimited polymorphic object not allowed"
2894 " in list directed I/O",
2895 CNULL);
2896 }
2897 if (DTYG(SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1))) == TY_DERIVED &&
2898 (A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(RHS(1))) == A_FUNC ||
2899 /* Allocate a temporary ast to store the value of the derived type array
2900 * reference whose subscript is a function reference, otherwise the
2901 * function would be incorrectly called in each component I/O. */
2902 (A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(RHS(1))) == A_SUBSCR &&
2903 A_CALLFGG(SST_ASTG(RHS(1)))))) {
2904 ast = sem_tempify(RHS(1));
2905 (void)add_stmt(ast);
2906 SST_IDP(RHS(1), S_IDENT);
2907 SST_ASTP(RHS(1), 0);
2908 SST_SYMP(RHS(1), A_SPTRG(A_DESTG(ast)));
2909 }
2910 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_DERIVED) {
2911 i = dtype_has_defined_io(dtype);
2912 if (i & (DT_IO_FWRITE | DT_IO_UWRITE)) {
2913 sem.defined_io_seen = 1;
2914 }
2915
2916 sptr1 = 0;
2917 if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_SCONST) {
2918 sptr1 = SST_SYMG(RHS(1));
2919 if (STYPEG(sptr1) == ST_TYPEDEF) {
2920 sptr =
2921 getcctmp_sc('t', sem.dtemps++, ST_VAR, SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1)), io_sc);
2922 sptr = init_derived_w_acl(sptr, SST_ACLG(RHS(1)));
2923 SST_IDP(RHS(1), S_IDENT);
2924 SST_ASTP(RHS(1), 0);
2925 SST_SYMP(RHS(1), sptr);
2926 SST_ALIASP(RHS(1), 0);
2927 SST_CVLENP(RHS(1), 0);
2928 SST_SHAPEP(RHS(1), 0);
2929 }
2930 }
2931 }
2932 goto io_item_shared;
2933 /*
2934 * <output item> ::= <elp> <output list> , <implied do control> )
2935 */
2936 case OUTPUT_ITEM2:
2937 goto implied_do_shared;
2938
2939 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2940 /*
2941 * <input list> ::= <input list> , <input item> |
2942 */
2943 case INPUT_LIST1:
2944 ((IOL *)SST_ENDG(RHS(1)))->next = (IOL *)SST_BEGG(RHS(3));
2945 SST_ENDP(RHS(1), SST_ENDG(RHS(3)));
2946 break;
2947 /*
2948 * <input list> ::= <input item>
2949 */
2950 case INPUT_LIST2:
2951 sem.defined_io_seen = 0;
2952 break;
2953
2954 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
2955 /*
2956 * <input item> ::= <var ref> |
2957 */
2958 case INPUT_ITEM1:
2959 if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) != S_DERIVED && !is_varref(RHS(1)))
2960 IOERR(214);
2961
2962 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1));
2963 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
2964 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
2965 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_DERIVED) {
2966 i = dtype_has_defined_io(dtype);
2967 if (i & (DT_IO_FREAD | DT_IO_UREAD)) {
2968 sem.defined_io_seen = 1;
2969 }
2970 }
2971
2972 io_item_shared:
2973 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1));
2974
2975 ast1 = ast3 = SST_ASTG(RHS(1));
2976 if (A_TYPEG(ast1) == A_SUBSTR)
2977 ast1 = A_LOPG(ast1);
2978 if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_LVALUE && DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY &&
2979 A_TYPEG(ast1) == A_SUBSCR) {
2980 /*
2981 * If an input item is an array section containing vector
2982 * subscripts, the dimensions containing the vector subscripts
2983 * must be scalarized. Ultimately, the io item will be classified
2984 * as an 'expression', and the ast for the item will be a subscript
2985 * ast bounded by do 'begin-end' pairs, one for each vector
2986 * subscript; if more than one vector subscript appears, the
2987 * resulting loops will be nested, where the left-most vector
2988 * subscript is the innermost loop, etc. The bounds of each do
2989 * are derived from the shape of the index vector.
2990 */
2991 IOL *iol_var; /* iol item representing the io item if any
2992 * vector subscripts are present.
2993 */
2994 LOGICAL isvec; /* any subscripts which are triples */
2995 LOGICAL ischar; /* base type is character */
2996 LOGICAL anydiff; /* any difficult subscripts found */
2997 LOGICAL anyvec; /* any vector subscripts found */
2998
2999 isvec = FALSE;
3000 ischar = FALSE;
3001 anydiff = FALSE;
3002 anyvec = FALSE;
3003 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
3004 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_CHAR || DTY(dtype) == TY_NCHAR)
3005 ischar = TRUE;
3006 iolptr = NULL; /* previous dobegin which was emitted */
3007 doend = NULL; /* last doend emitted */
3008 asd = A_ASDG(ast1);
3009 numdim = ASD_NDIM(asd); /* get number of subscripts */
3010 for (i = 0; i < numdim; i++) {
3011 int asd2;
3012 /* look for difficult subscripts */
3013 ast2 = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
3014 switch (A_TYPEG(ast2)) {
3015 case A_ID:
3016 case A_TRIPLE:
3017 break;
3018 case A_SUBSCR:
3019 /* if only a single dimension with triplet subscript, ok */
3020 asd2 = A_ASDG(ast2);
3021 if (ASD_NDIM(asd2) != 1) {
3022 anydiff = TRUE;
3023 } else if (A_TYPEG(ASD_SUBS(asd2, 0)) != A_TRIPLE) {
3024 anydiff = TRUE;
3025 }
3026 break;
3027 default:
3028 if (A_SHAPEG(ast2))
3029 anydiff = TRUE;
3030 }
3031 }
3032 for (i = 0; !anydiff && i < numdim; i++) {
3033 int shp;
3034 ast2 = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
3035 if (A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_TRIPLE && !ischar)
3036 isvec = TRUE;
3037 else if ((shp = A_SHAPEG(ast2)) ||
3038 (ischar && A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_TRIPLE)) {
3039 IOL *iol_tmp;
3040 anyvec = TRUE;
3041 /* vector subscript */
3042 if (iolptr == NULL) {
3043 /* create the semantic stack and IOL representing the
3044 * subscripted form of the input item.
3045 */
3046 stkptr = (SST *)getitem(0, sizeof(SST));
3047 *stkptr = *RHS(1);
3048 iol_var = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3049 iol_var->id = IE_EXPR;
3050 iol_var->next = NULL;
3051 iol_var->element = stkptr;
3052 iol_var->l_std = 0;
3053 iolptr = iol_var;
3054 }
3055 /* create a DOINFO record for this vector; the index
3056 * variable is a compiler-created temporary and the bounds
3057 * are extracted from the shape of the index vector.
3058 */
3059 doinfo = get_doinfo(0);
3060 sptr = get_temp(DT_INT);
3061 doinfo->index_var = sptr;
3062 if (A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_TRIPLE) {
3063 doinfo->init_expr = A_LBDG(ast2);
3064 doinfo->limit_expr = A_UPBDG(ast2);
3065 doinfo->step_expr = A_STRIDEG(ast2);
3066 if (doinfo->step_expr == 0)
3067 doinfo->step_expr = astb.i1;
3068 } else {
3069 doinfo->init_expr = SHD_LWB(shp, 0);
3070 doinfo->limit_expr = SHD_UPB(shp, 0);
3071 doinfo->step_expr = SHD_STRIDE(shp, 0);
3072 }
3073 doinfo->count =
3074 mk_binop(OP_SUB, doinfo->limit_expr, doinfo->init_expr, DT_INT);
3075 doinfo->count =
3076 mk_binop(OP_ADD, doinfo->count, doinfo->step_expr, DT_INT);
3077 doinfo->count =
3078 mk_binop(OP_DIV, doinfo->count, doinfo->step_expr, DT_INT);
3079 /*
3080 * Create the DOBEGIN IOL for this index. Its 'next'
3081 * pointer is just the previous dobegin or the IOL
3082 * of the subscripted form.
3083 */
3084 dobegin = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3085 dobegin->id = IE_DOBEGIN;
3086 dobegin->next = iolptr;
3087 dobegin->doinfo = doinfo;
3088 dobegin->l_std = 0;
3089 /*
3090 * Create the DOEND IOL for this index; ensure that
3091 * the previous doend, if present, is linked to this doend.
3092 * If this is the first do pair, the IOL representing the
3093 * item is linked to this doend.
3094 */
3095 iol_tmp = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3096 if (doend)
3097 doend->next = iol_tmp;
3098 else
3099 iolptr->next = iol_tmp;
3100 doend = iol_tmp;
3101 doend->id = IE_DOEND;
3102 doend->next = NULL;
3103 doend->doinfo = doinfo;
3104 doend->l_std = 0;
3105 iolptr = dobegin;
3106 /*
3107 * prepare the subscript for this dimension; it's just
3108 * a subscripted reference of the index vector and the
3109 * subscript is the DO index variable.
3110 */
3111 dum = mk_id(sptr);
3112 if (A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_TRIPLE) {
3113 ast2 = dum;
3114 } else if (A_TYPEG(ast2) == A_SUBSCR) {
3115 /* must have been single subscript */
3116 ast2 = mk_subscr(A_LOPG(ast2), &dum, 1, DT_INT);
3117 } else {
3118 ast2 = mk_subscr(ast2, &dum, 1, DT_INT);
3119 }
3120 }
3121 subs[i] = ast2;
3122 }
3123 if (iolptr) {
3124 /* vector subscripts were found; if any triples were present,
3125 * the type of the reference is still array
3126 */
3127 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1));
3128 if (!isvec)
3129 dtype = DTY(dtype + 1);
3130 /*
3131 * Create the subscripted form of the io item; fill in the
3132 * item's semantic stack entry.
3133 */
3134 ast1 = mk_subscr((int)A_LOPG(ast1), subs, numdim, dtype);
3135 stkptr = iol_var->element;
3136 SST_IDP(stkptr, S_LVALUE);
3137 SST_DTYPEP(stkptr, dtype);
3138 /* if this is a substring, recreate the substring */
3139 if (A_TYPEG(ast3) == A_SUBSTR)
3140 ast1 = mk_substr(ast1, A_LEFTG(ast3), A_RIGHTG(ast3), dtype);
3141
3142 SST_ASTP(stkptr, ast1);
3143 if (!isvec)
3144 SST_SHAPEP(stkptr, 0);
3145 /*
3146 * define the begin and end fields for this item; they are
3147 * just the last dobegin and doend IOLs created.
3148 */
3149 SST_BEGP(LHS, (ITEM *)dobegin);
3150 SST_ENDP(LHS, (ITEM *)doend);
3151 break;
3152 }
3153 }
3154 count = 0;
3155 sptr1 = 0;
3156 if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_IDENT || SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_DERIVED)
3157 sptr1 = SST_SYMG(RHS(1));
3158 else if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_LVALUE)
3159 sptr1 = SST_LSYMG(RHS(1));
3160
3161 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1));
3162 if (sptr1 && DTYG(dtype) == TY_DERIVED) {
3163 /* derived, get_derived_iolptrs() sets up LHS with a list of
3164 iolptrs representing the derived object*/
3165
3166 dtype = DDTG(DTYPEG(sptr1));
3167 if (dtype_has_defined_io(dtype) & functype[is_read][fmttyp]) {
3168 stkptr = (SST *)getitem(0, sizeof(SST));
3169 *stkptr = *RHS(1);
3170 iolptr = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3171 iolptr->id = IE_EXPR;
3172 iolptr->next = NULL;
3173 iolptr->element = stkptr;
3174 iolptr->l_std = 0;
3175 SST_BEGP(LHS, (ITEM *)iolptr);
3176 SST_ENDP(LHS, (ITEM *)iolptr);
3177
3178 break;
3179 }
3180 (void)mkarg(RHS(1), &dum);
3181 sptr1 = refsym(sptr1, OC_OTHER);
3182 SST_SYMP(RHS(1), sptr1);
3183 get_derived_iolptrs(LHS, sptr1, RHS(1));
3184 } else {
3185 /*
3186 * guard against the item being c_loc()
3187 */
3188 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_DERIVED && A_TYPEG(ast1) == A_INTR &&
3189 is_iso_cptr(dtype)) {
3190 error(155, 3, gbl.lineno,
3191 "A derived type containing private "
3192 "components cannot be an I/O item",
3193 CNULL);
3194 }
3195 stkptr = (SST *)getitem(0, sizeof(SST));
3196 *stkptr = *RHS(1);
3197 iolptr = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3198 iolptr->id = IE_EXPR;
3199 iolptr->next = NULL;
3200 iolptr->element = stkptr;
3201 iolptr->l_std = 0;
3202 SST_BEGP(LHS, (ITEM *)iolptr);
3203 SST_ENDP(LHS, (ITEM *)iolptr);
3204 }
3205 break;
3206 /*
3207 * <input item> ::= <elp> <input list> ) |
3208 */
3209 case INPUT_ITEM2:
3210 *LHS = *RHS(2);
3211 break;
3212 /*
3213 * <input item> ::= <elp> <input list> , <implied do control> )
3214 */
3215 case INPUT_ITEM3:
3216 implied_do_shared:
3217 doinfo = (DOINFO *)SST_BEGG(RHS(4));
3218 sptr = doinfo->index_var;
3219 if (flg.smp || flg.accmp)
3220 is_dovar_sptr(doinfo->index_var);
3221 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3222 iolptr = (IOL *)SST_BEGG(RHS(2));
3223
3224 if (DT_ISINT(dtype) && iolptr == (IOL *)SST_ENDG(RHS(2)) &&
3225 iolptr->id == IE_EXPR) {
3226 /*
3227 * check for an optimizable DO loop; the conditions which must be
3228 * satisfied are:
3229 * 1. The DO index is integer.
3230 * 2. the I/O list consists of a single subscripted array without
3231 * a substring specification. Also, the array may not be a
3232 * structure member.
3233 * 3. one subscript is the DO index variable.
3234 * 4. the remaining subscripts are either ICON or ILD of a variable
3235 * not the DO index variable.
3236 * 5. no subscript checking
3237 */
3238
3239 /*
3240 * Determine if the I/O list item is a subscripted array --
3241 */
3242 stkptr = iolptr->element;
3243 if (SST_IDG(stkptr) == S_IDENT || SST_IDG(stkptr) == S_CONST ||
3244 SST_IDG(stkptr) == S_ACONST)
3245 goto not_optz;
3246 ast1 = SST_ASTG(stkptr);
3247 if (A_TYPEG(ast1) != A_SUBSCR)
3248 goto not_optz;
3249 if (DTY(A_DTYPEG(ast1)) == TY_CHAR || !DT_ISBASIC(A_DTYPEG(ast1)))
3250 goto not_optz;
3251 asd = A_ASDG(ast1);
3252
3253 /* scan through the subscripts */
3254
3255 numdim = ASD_NDIM(asd); /* get number of subscripts */
3256 dim = -1;
3257 for (i = 0; i < numdim; i++) {
3258 ast2 = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
3259 switch (A_TYPEG(ast2)) {
3260 case A_CNST: /* constant is okay */
3261 break;
3262 case A_ID: /* check load */
3263 if (A_SPTRG(ast2) != sptr)
3264 break;
3265 if (dim >= 0) /* another use of index */
3266 goto not_optz;
3267 dim = i;
3268 break; /* subscript is okay */
3269 case A_CONV:
3270 ast3 = A_LOPG(ast2);
3271 if (A_TYPEG(ast3) != A_ID || A_SPTRG(ast3) != sptr || dim >= 0) {
3272 goto not_optz;
3273 }
3274 dim = i;
3275 break;
3276 default: /* anything else is not okay */
3277 goto not_optz;
3278 }
3279 subs[i] = ast2; /* remember subscript just in case */
3280 }
3281 if (dim < 0) /* index variable not used as subscript */
3282 goto not_optz;
3283 /*
3284 * Finally have determined that the implied DO can be optimized
3285 * into a single call -- a new subscript ast needs to be created
3286 * with a triple replacing the index variable in the corresponding
3287 * dimension. The triple will represent the section
3288 * <init_expr>:<limit_expr>:<step_expr>.
3289 * All other dimension will have a triple of <subs>:<subs>.
3290 */
3291 for (i = 0; i < numdim; i++)
3292 if (i == dim) {
3293 int l, u, s;
3294 l = doinfo->init_expr;
3295 u = doinfo->limit_expr;
3296 s = doinfo->step_expr;
3297 if (XBIT(68, 0x1) && A_DTYPEG(subs[dim]) == DT_INT8 &&
3298 size_of(A_DTYPEG(l)) < 8) {
3299 l = mk_convert(l, DT_INT8);
3300 u = mk_convert(u, DT_INT8);
3301 if (s)
3302 s = mk_convert(s, DT_INT8);
3303 }
3304 subs[dim] = mk_triple(l, u, s);
3305 } else
3306 subs[i] = ASD_SUBS(asd, i);
3307 ast1 = mk_subscr((int)A_LOPG(ast1), subs, numdim,
3308 (int)A_DTYPEG(A_LOPG(ast1)));
3309
3310 SST_DTYPEP(stkptr, A_DTYPEG(ast1));
3311 SST_ASTP(stkptr, ast1);
3312 iolptr->id = IE_OPTDO;
3313 iolptr->doinfo = doinfo;
3314 *LHS = *RHS(2);
3315 break;
3316 }
3317
3318 not_optz:
3319 dobegin = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3320 dobegin->id = IE_DOBEGIN;
3321 dobegin->next = iolptr;
3322 dobegin->doinfo = doinfo;
3323 dobegin->l_std = 0;
3324 doend = (IOL *)getitem(0, sizeof(IOL));
3325 doend->id = IE_DOEND;
3326 doend->next = NULL;
3327 doend->doinfo = doinfo;
3328 doend->l_std = 0;
3329
3330 SST_BEGP(LHS, (ITEM *)dobegin);
3331 ((IOL *)(SST_ENDG(RHS(2))))->next = doend;
3332 SST_ENDP(LHS, (ITEM *)doend);
3333 /*
3334 * STDs could have been added since the beginning left paren.
3335 * Since the DO begin is generated later in the parse, these STDs
3336 * will appear before the DO. For the STDs added since the beginning
3337 * left paren, remove these from the STD list and attach them to the
3338 * dobegin; when the DO is generated these STDs will be added after the
3339 * DO begin. Examples of when STDs may be added are when referencing
3340 * functions/intrinsics which turn into 'calls'.
3341 */
3342 {
3343 int s, s1, s2, t;
3344 s = SST_ASTG(RHS(1)); /* STD generated when left paren seen */
3345 s1 = STD_NEXT(s); /* STD generated after left paren */
3346 s2 = SST_ASTG(RHS(4)); /* STD generated before do expressions*/
3347 if (s != s2) {
3348 /* Unlink the list of stds added after the left paren and
3349 * before the implied do expressions and add to the dobegin's
3350 * iol structure. Stds s1 through s2, inclusive, mark the
3351 * list to be moved.
3352 *
3353 * Before:
3354 * s <-> s1 <-> ... <-> s2 <-> t
3355 * After:
3356 * s s1 <-> ... <-> s2 t
3357 * | |
3358 * +<------------------------->+
3359 */
3360 dobegin->l_std = s1;
3361 t = STD_NEXT(s2);
3362 STD_NEXT(s) = t;
3363 STD_PREV(t) = s;
3364 STD_NEXT(s2) = 0;
3365 } else
3366 dobegin->l_std = 0;
3367 }
3368
3369 break;

3372 /*
3373 * <format stmt> ::= <format> ( <format list> ) |
3374 */
3375 case FORMAT_STMT1:
3376 end_format:
3377 put_edit(FED_END); /* note that the last rp is not put out */
3378 PUT(rescan);

3383 dinit_put(DINIT_END, 0);

3402 if (scn.currlab == 0)

3404 sptr = get_fmt_array(scn.currlab, ST_VAR);
3405 FMTPTP(scn.currlab, sptr);
3406 DEFDP(scn.currlab, 1);
3407 scn.currlab = 0;
3408 sptr1 = SST_SYMG(RHS(2));
3409 DTYPEP(sptr, DTYPEG(sptr1));

3546 case FORMAT_ITEM6:

3565 /*

3569 break;
3570 /*
3571 * <format item> ::= <repeat factor> <F2 item> |
3572 */
3573 case FORMAT_ITEM8:
3574 break;
3575 /*
3576 * <format item> ::= <scale factor> |
3577 */
3578 case FORMAT_ITEM9:
3579 put_edit(FED_P);
3580 put_ffield(RHS(1));
3581 break;
3582 /*
3583 * <format item> ::= <F3 item>
3584 */
3585 case FORMAT_ITEM10:
3586 break;
3587 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
3588 /*
3589 * <repeat factor> ::= |
3590 */
3591 case REPEAT_FACTOR1:
3592 break;
3593 /*
3594 * <repeat factor> ::= <ffield>
3595 */
3596 case REPEAT_FACTOR2:
3597 lastrpt = fasize;
3598 put_ffield(RHS(1));
3599 if (SST_IDG(RHS(1)) == S_CONST && SST_CVALG(RHS(1)) == 0)
3600 IOERR(206);
3601 break;
3602
3603 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
3604 /*
3605 * <scale factor> ::= <ffield> P |
3606 */
3607 case SCALE_FACTOR1:
3608 break;
3609 /*
3610 * <scale factor> ::= <addop> <ffield> P
3611 */
3612 case SCALE_FACTOR2:
3613 if (SST_OPTYPEG(RHS(1)) == OP_ADD)
3614 *LHS = *RHS(2);
3615 else { /* negate <ffield> */
3616#if DEBUG
3617 assert(SST_IDG(RHS(2)) == S_CONST, "semantio:exp.-<const>P", 0, 3);
3618#endif
3619 SST_IDP(LHS, S_CONST);
3620 SST_CVALP(LHS, -SST_CVALG(RHS(2)));
3621 SST_ASTP(LHS, mk_cval(SST_CVALG(LHS), DT_INT));

3623 break;

3649 put_ffield(RHS(4));

3764 CNULL, CNULL);
3765 rescan = SST_RNG2G(RHS(1));
3766 put_edit(FED_RPAREN);
3767 PUT(SST_RNG1G(RHS(1)));

3773 */
3774 case FLP1:

3776 * left paren */

3779 * a repeat count immediately preceded the paren. locate the
3780 * repeat count for the run-time (marks reversion).

3783 else

3786 put_edit(FED_LPAREN);

3796 put_ffield(RHS(4));
3797 break;

3800 */
3801 case F2_ITEM2:
3802 put_edit(FED_Ew_d);
3803 put_ffield(RHS(2));
3804 put_ffield(RHS(4));
3805 break;
3806 /*

3808 */
3809 case F2_ITEM3:
3810 if (SST_CVALG(RHS(2)) == 0) {
3811 put_edit(FED_G0_d);
3812 } else {
3813 put_edit(FED_Gw_d);
3814 }
3815 put_ffield(RHS(2));
3816 put_ffield(RHS(4));

3866 case F2_ITEM9:
3867 put_edit(FED_D);
3868 break;

3884 break;

3888 case F2_ITEM12:
3889 put_edit(FED_DT);
3890 PUT(0);
3891 PUT(1);
3892 sptr = getstring("DT", 2);
3893 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3894 len = string_length(dtype);
3895 PUT(0);
3896 PUT(len);
3897 dinit_put(DT_CHAR, (INT)sptr);
3898 if (DTY(DT_INT) == TY_INT8) {
3899 len = (len + 7) & ~7;
3900 fasize += len >> 3;
3901 } else {
3902 len = (len + 3) & ~3;
3903 fasize += len >> 2;
3904 }
3905
3906 break;
3907 /*
3908 * <F2 item> ::= DT <dts>
3909 */
3910 case F2_ITEM13:
3911 put_edit(FED_DT);
3912
3913 if (SST_BEGG(RHS(2)) == 0 && SST_ENDG(RHS(2)) == 0) {
3914 char *str;
3915 /* <char_literal> */
3916
3917 PUT(0);
3918 PUT(1);
3919 sptr = SST_SYMG(RHS(2));
3920 sptr = A_SPTRG(SST_ASTG(RHS(2)));
3921 strptr = malloc(strlen(stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr)) + 3);
3922
3923 str = strcpy(strptr, "DT");
3924 str = strcat(strptr, stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr));
3925 sptr = getstring(str, strlen(strptr));
3926 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3927 len = string_length(dtype);
3928 PUT(0);
3929 PUT(len);
3930 dinit_put(DT_CHAR, (INT)sptr);
3931 /* pad out data init if len not divisible by 8 */
3932 if (DTY(DT_INT) == TY_INT8) {
3933 len = (len + 7) & ~7;
3934 fasize += len >> 3;
3935 } else {
3936 len = (len + 3) & ~3;
3937 fasize += len >> 2;
3938 }
3939
3940 } else if (SST_IDG(RHS(2)) == -1) {
3941 /* <vlist> */
3942 PUT(0);
3943 PUT(2);
3944 sptr = getstring("DT", 2);
3945 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3946 len = string_length(dtype);
3947 PUT(0);
3948 PUT(len);
3949 dinit_put(DT_CHAR, (INT)sptr);
3950 if (DTY(DT_INT) == TY_INT8) {
3951 len = (len + 7) & ~7;
3952 fasize += len >> 3;
3953 } else {
3954 len = (len + 3) & ~3;
3955 fasize += len >> 2;
3956 }
3957 put_vlist(RHS(2));
3958 break;
3959 } else {
3960 /* <char_literal> <vlist> */
3961 char *str;
3962 PUT(0);
3963 PUT(2);
3964 /*strcpy */
3965 sptr = A_SPTRG(SST_ASTG(RHS(2)));
3966 strptr = malloc(strlen(stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr)) + 3);
3967 str = strcpy(strptr, "DT");
3968 str = strcat(strptr, stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(sptr));
3969
3970 sptr = getstring(str, strlen(str));
3971 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr);
3972 len = string_length(dtype);
3973 PUT(0);
3974 PUT(len);
3975 dinit_put(DT_CHAR, (INT)sptr);
3976 /* pad out data init if len not divisible by 8 */
3977 if (DTY(DT_INT) == TY_INT8) {
3978 len = (len + 7) & ~7;
3979 fasize += len >> 3;
3980 } else {
3981 len = (len + 3) & ~3;
3982 fasize += len >> 2;
3983 }
3984 put_vlist(RHS(2));
3985 }
3986
3987 break;
3988 /*
3989 * <F2 item> ::= <g0format>
3990 */
3991 case F2_ITEM14:
3992 put_edit(FED_G0);
3993 break;
3994
3995
3996 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
3997 /*
3998 * <F3 item> ::= T <ffield> |
3999 */
4000 case F3_ITEM1:
4001 put_edit(FED_T);
4002 put_ffield(RHS(2));
4003 break;
4004 /*
4005 * <F3 item> ::= TL <ffield> |
4006 */
4007 case F3_ITEM2:
4008 put_edit(FED_TL);
4009 put_ffield(RHS(2));
4010 break;
4011 /*
4012 * <F3 item> ::= TR <ffield> |
4013 */
4014 case F3_ITEM3:
4015 put_edit(FED_TR);
4016 put_ffield(RHS(2));
4017 break;
4018 /*
4019 * <F3 item> ::= <ffield> X |
4020 */
4021 case F3_ITEM4:
4022 put_edit(FED_X);
4023 put_ffield(RHS(1));
4024 break;
4025 /*
4026 * <F3 item> ::= X |
4027 */
4028 case F3_ITEM5:
4029 put_edit(FED_X);
4030 PUT(0);
4031 PUT(1);
4032 break;
4033 /*
4034 * <F3 item> ::= S |
4035 */
4036 case F3_ITEM6:
4037 put_edit(FED_S);
4038 break;
4039 /*
4040 * <F3 item> ::= SP |
4041 */
4042 case F3_ITEM7:
4043 put_edit(FED_SP);
4044 break;
4045 /*
4046 * <F3 item> ::= SS |
4047 */
4048 case F3_ITEM8:
4049 put_edit(FED_SS);
4050 break;
4051 /*
4052 * <F3 item> ::= BN |
4053 */
4054 case F3_ITEM9:
4055 put_edit(FED_BN);
4056 break;
4057 /*
4058 * <F3 item> ::= BZ |
4059 */
4060 case F3_ITEM10:
4061 put_edit(FED_BZ);
4062 break;
4063 /*
4064 * <F3 item> ::= DC |
4065 */
4066 case F3_ITEM11:
4067 put_edit(FED_DC);
4068 break;
4069 /*
4070 * <F3 item> ::= DP |
4071 */
4072 case F3_ITEM12:
4073 put_edit(FED_DP);
4074 break;
4075 /*
4076 * <F3 item> ::= Q |
4077 */
4078 case F3_ITEM13:
4079 put_edit(FED_Q);
4080 break;
4081 /*
4082 * <F3 item> ::= '$' |
4083 */
4084 case F3_ITEM14:
4085 put_edit(FED_DOLLAR);
4086 break;
4087 /*
4088 * <F3 item> ::= RU |
4089 */
4090 case F3_ITEM15:
4091 put_edit(FED_RU);
4092 break;
4093 /*
4094 * <F3 item> ::= RD |
4095 */
4096 case F3_ITEM16:
4097 put_edit(FED_RD);
4098 break;
4099 /*
4100 * <F3 item> ::= RZ |
4101 */
4102 case F3_ITEM17:
4103 put_edit(FED_RZ);
4104 break;
4105 /*
4106 * <F3 item> ::= RN |
4107 */
4108 case F3_ITEM18:
4109 put_edit(FED_RN);
4110 break;
4111 /*
4112 * <F3 item> ::= RC |
4113 */
4114 case F3_ITEM19:
4115 put_edit(FED_RC);
4116 break;
4117 /*
4118 * <F3 item> ::= RP
4119 */
4120 case F3_ITEM20:
4121 put_edit(FED_RP);
4122 break;
4123 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
4124 /*
4125 * <dts> ::= <char_literal>
4126 */
4127 case DTS1:
4128 SST_CVALP(LHS, SST_CVALG(RHS(1)));
4129 SST_IDP(LHS, S_CONST);
4130 SST_DTYPEP(LHS, SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1)));
4131 SST_ASTP(LHS, mk_cval(SST_CVALG(LHS), SST_DTYPEG(RHS(1))));
4132 SST_SYMP(LHS, A_SPTRG(SST_ASTG(LHS)));
4133
4134 SST_ENDP(LHS, 0);
4135 SST_BEGP(LHS, 0);
4136
4137 break;
4138 /*
4139 * <dts> ::= <char_literal> <dlp> <dt vlist> )
4140 */
4141 case DTS2:
4142 SST_BEGP(LHS, SST_BEGG(RHS(3)));
4143 SST_ENDP(LHS, SST_ENDG(RHS(3)));
4144
4145 break;
4146 /*
4147 * <dts> ::= <dlp> <dt vlist> )
4148 */
4149 case DTS3:
4150 *LHS = *RHS(2);
4151 SST_IDP(LHS, -1);
4152
4153 break;
4154
4155 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
4156 /*
4157 * <dt vlist> ::= <dt vlist> , <addop> <integer>
4158 * <dt vlist> ::= <dt vlist> , <integer>
4159 * <dt vlist> ::= <addop> <integer>
4160 * <dt vlist> ::= <integer>
4161 */
4162 case DT_VLIST1:
4163 case DT_VLIST2:
4164 case DT_VLIST3:
4165 case DT_VLIST4:
4166 count = DT_VLIST4 + 1 - rednum; // RHS symbol count: 4, 3, 2, or 1
4167 if ((count == 2 || count == 4) && SST_OPTYPEG(RHS(count - 1)) == OP_SUB)
4168 SST_CVALP(RHS(count), -SST_CVALG(RHS(count))); // negate <integer>
4169 e1 = (SST *)getitem(0, sizeof(SST));
4170 *e1 = *RHS(count);
4171 itemp = (ITEM *)getitem(0, sizeof(ITEM));
4172 itemp->next = ITEM_END;
4173 itemp->t.stkp = e1;
4174 if (count <= 2) {
4175 SST_BEGP(LHS, itemp);
4176 } else {
4177 (SST_ENDG(RHS(1)))->next = itemp;
4178 }
4179 SST_ENDP(LHS, itemp);
4180
4181 break;
4182
4183 /* ------------------------------------------------------------------ */
4184 /*
4185 * <ffield> ::= <integer>
4186 */
4187 case FFIELD1:
4188 SST_IDP(LHS, S_CONST);
4189 SST_ASTP(LHS, mk_cval(SST_CVALG(LHS), DT_INT));
4190 SST_DTYPEP(LHS, DT_INT);
4191 break;
4192
4193 /*
4194 * <unlimited format item> ::= <star repeat> <flp> <format list> )
4195 */
4196 case UNLIMITED_FORMAT_ITEM1:
4197 rescan = SST_RNG2G(RHS(2));
4198 put_edit(FED_RPAREN);
4199 PUT(SST_RNG1G(RHS(2)));
4200 break;
4201
4202 /*
4203 * <star repeat> ::= *
4204 */
4205 case STAR_REPEAT1:
4206 lastrpt = fasize;
4207 PUT(0);
4208 PUT(0x7fffffff);
4209 break;
4210
4211 default:
4212 interr("semantio: bad rednum ", rednum, 3);
4213 break;
4214 }
4215 return;
4216
4217end_IO_STMT:
4218 /*
4219 * common termination point for all I/O statments.
4220 */
4221 if (gbl.currsub && PUREG(gbl.currsub) && external_io)
4222 error(155, 2, gbl.lineno, SYMNAME(gbl.currsub),
4223 "- PURE subprograms may not contain external I/O statements");
4224 sem.io_stmt = FALSE;
4225 SST_ASTP(LHS, 0);
4226}
4227
4228static int
4229set_io_sc(void)
4230{
4231 io_sc = SC_LOCAL;
4232 if (sem.task)
4233 io_sc = SC_PRIVATE;
4234 return io_sc;
4235}
4236
4237/*
4238 * 'array_ast' is a character variable used as an internal I/O unit.
4239 * Its type is either:
4240 * A_SUBSCR: a regular section of a character array, or
4241 * A_SUBSTR: a substring whose parent is a regular section of a char array.
4242 * This copies 'array_ast' to a contiguous temporary array. The
4243 * temporary array is replicated, as is the original array, since
4244 * distribution of character arrays isn't supported.
4245 */
4246static int
4247copy_replic_sect_to_tmp(int array_ast)
4248{
4249 int asn, std, tmp_ast, tmp_sptr;
4250 int dtype;
4251 int eldtype;
4252 int subscr[7];
4253
4254 /* allocate(tmp(...))
4255 * tmp = array
4256 */
4257 switch (A_TYPEG(array_ast)) {
4258 case A_SUBSCR: /* a regular section */
4259 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr_of_subscript(array_ast));
4260 break;
4261 default: /* a substring of a regular section or just some array */
4262 dtype = A_DTYPEG(array_ast);
4263 break;
4264 }
4265 eldtype = DDTG(dtype);
4266 tmp_sptr = mk_shape_sptr(A_SHAPEG(array_ast), subscr, eldtype);
4267 tmp_ast = mk_id(tmp_sptr);
4268
4269 asn = mk_assn_stmt(tmp_ast, array_ast, eldtype);
4270 std = add_stmt(asn);
4271
4272 mk_mem_allocate(tmp_ast, subscr, std, array_ast);
4273 /* ...we call this after 'std = add_stmt( forall )' because
4274 * it adds stmts *before* 'std', so 'std' must be defined! */
4275
4276 return tmp_ast;
4277}
4278
4279/*
4280 * Copies back the temporary array created by a prior call to
4281 * 'copy_replic_sect_to_tmp' to the original regular section.
4282 */
4283static void
4284copy_back_to_replic_sect(int array_ast, int tmp_ast)
4285{
4286 int asn, std;
4287 int dtype;
4288 int eldtype;
4289
4290 /* array = tmp
4291 * deallocate(tmp)
4292 */
4293 switch (A_TYPEG(array_ast)) {
4294 case A_SUBSCR: /* a regular section */
4295 dtype = DTYPEG(sptr_of_subscript(array_ast));
4296 break;
4297 default: /* a substring of a regular section or just some array */
4298 dtype = A_DTYPEG(array_ast);
4299 break;
4300 }
4301 eldtype = DDTG(dtype);
4302 asn = mk_assn_stmt(array_ast, tmp_ast, eldtype);
4303
4304 std = add_stmt_after(asn, STD_LAST);
4305
4306 mk_mem_deallocate(tmp_ast, std);
4307}
4308
4309/* ensure iostat locates an AST */
4310static void
4311fix_iostat(void)
4312{
4313 if (PTV(PT_IOSTAT) == 0)
4314 PTV(PT_IOSTAT) = astb.i0;
4315}
4316
4317static int
4318chk_SIZE_var()
4319{
4320 int asn = 0;
4321
4322 if (PTS(PT_SIZE) && PTTMPUSED(PT_SIZE) && PTVARREF(PT_SIZE) != 1) {
4323 /* if SIZE specified, assign SIZE tmp back to user data item */
4324 asn = mk_assn_stmt(PTVARREF(PT_SIZE),
4325 mk_convert(PTV(PT_SIZE), A_DTYPEG(PTVARREF(PT_SIZE))),
4326 A_DTYPEG(PTVARREF(PT_SIZE)));
4327 }
4328 return asn;
4329}
4330
4331/* Add test and branches for ERR=, END=, and EOR=. */
4332static int
4333add_cgoto(int ast)
4334{
4335 int lbsptr;
4336 int last_ast;
4337 int inquire_cnt = 13;
4338
4339 if (A_TYPEG(ast) == A_ASN)
4340 ast = A_DESTG(ast);
4341 last_ast = 0;
4342 if (strcmp(SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(io_call.ast))),
4343 mkRteRtnNm(RTE_f90io_fmtr_end)) == 0 ||
4344 strncmp(SYMNAME(A_SPTRG(A_LOPG(io_call.ast))),
4345 mkRteRtnNm(RTE_f90io_inquirea), inquire_cnt) == 0) {
4346 int asn = chk_SIZE_var();
4347 if (asn) {
4348 add_stmt_after(asn, (int)STD_PREV(0));
4349 PT_TMPUSED(PT_SIZE, 0);
4350 }
4351 }
4352 if ((lbsptr = PTV(PT_ERR)) != 0) /* == 1 => error */
4353 last_ast = end_or_err(ast, lbsptr, astb.i1);
4354 if ((lbsptr = PTV(PT_END)) != 0) /* == 2 ==> end of file */
4355 last_ast = end_or_err(ast, lbsptr, mk_cval((INT)2, DT_INT));
4356 if ((lbsptr = PTV(PT_EOR)) != 0) /* == 3 ==> end of record */
4357 last_ast = end_or_err(ast, lbsptr, mk_cval((INT)3, DT_INT));
4358
4359 return last_ast;
4360}
4361
4362/* src - ast of variable assigned the value of the func */
4363/* elab - label of END=, ERR=, or EOR= */
4364/* eqval - ast of value which is compared with for equality */
4365/*
4366 * END= or ERR=; generate the ast sequence to test the value of an
4367 * i/o function and branch to the END=, ERR=, or EOR= label. We're
4368 * always comparing for inequality):
4369 * if ( io_call() .neq. eqval ) goto no-error-lab
4370 * <code to set-up/clean-up for error>
4371 * goto err_lab
4372 * no-error-lab:
4373 * NOTE: must end an i/o critical section if end or err is taken.
4374 */
4375static int
4376end_or_err(int src, int elab, int eqval)
4377{
4378 int tmp, ast2;
4379 int ast;
4380 int astlab;
4381 int std;
4382 int sz_asgn = chk_SIZE_var();
4383 int no_error, ifexpr;
4384
4385 tmp = mk_binop(OP_EQ, src, eqval, DT_LOG);
4386 /*
4387 * if condition is false, branch to no-error case - branch around
4388 * critical section code code.
4389 */
4390
4391 no_error = getlab();
4392 ast = mk_stmt(A_IF, 0);
4393 ifexpr = mk_unop(OP_LNOT, tmp, DT_LOG);
4394 A_IFEXPRP(ast, ifexpr);
4395 ast2 = mk_stmt(A_GOTO, 0);
4396 astlab = mk_label(no_error);
4397 A_L1P(ast2, astlab);
4398 A_IFSTMTP(ast, ast2);
4399 ast = add_stmt_after(ast, (int)STD_PREV(0));
4400 if (sz_asgn) {
4401 add_stmt_after(sz_asgn, (int)STD_PREV(0));
4402 }
4403 ast = fio_end_err(0, elab); /* fall-thru to critical section end & br code */
4404 RFCNTI(no_error);
4405 ast = mk_stmt(A_CONTINUE, 0);
4406 std = add_stmt_after(ast, (int)STD_PREV(0));
4407 STD_LABEL(std) = no_error;
4408
4409 return ast;
4410}
4411
4412/*
4413 * If a ERR= or END= is taken and we need to "end" the i/o critical section,
4414 * a special block is written:
4415 * new-err/end-label:
4416 * fio_end();
4417 * goto err/end-label;
4418 * NOTE that the conditional branch has been changed to reflect the new
4419 * label.
4420 */
4421/* lab - label of block of code to call fio_end & branch;
4422 * may be 0 -- block is not labeled
4423 */
4424/* elab - label of branch target */
4425static int
4426fio_end_err(int lab, int elab)
4427{
4428 int ast;
4429 int astlab;
4430 if (flg.smp || flg.accmp || XBIT(125, 0x1)) {
4431 if (flg.smp || flg.accmp)
4432 begin_io_call(A_CALL, sym_mkfunc_nodesc("_mp_ecs_nest", DT_NONE), 0);
4433 else
4434 (void)begin_io_call(A_CALL, mk_iofunc(RTE_f90io_end, DT_NONE, 0), 0);
4435 ast = end_io_call();
4436 }
4437 if (lab)
4438 STD_LABEL(A_STDG(ast)) = lab;
4439 ast = mk_stmt(A_GOTO, 0);
4440 astlab = mk_label(elab);
4441 A_L1P(ast, astlab);
4442 (void)add_stmt_after(ast, (int)STD_PREV(0));
4443
4444 return ast;
4445}
4446
4447static void
4448chk_expr(SST *stk, int p, int dtype)
4449{
4450 int dt;
4451
4452 if (PTV(p))
4453 IOERR2(202, PTNAME(p));
4454
4455 if (is_varref(stk))
4456 PT_VARREF(p, 1);
4457
4458 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_CHAR || DTY(dtype) == TY_NCHAR)
4459 (void)mkarg(stk, &dt);
4460 else if (DT_ISINT(dtype)) {
4461 (void)chktyp(stk, dtype, FALSE);
4462 dt = SST_DTYPEG(stk);
4463 } else { /* pass by value: */
4464 (void)mkexpr(stk);
4465 dt = SST_DTYPEG(stk);
4466 }
4467 if (DTY(dt) != DTY(dtype))
4468 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(p));
4469 PTV(p) = SST_ASTG(stk);
4470}

4472static void
4473gen_spec_item_tmp(SST *stk, int p, int dtype)
4474{

4476 int sptr;
4477 int i;
4478
4479 (void)mkarg(stk, &dt);
4480 PT_VARREF(p, SST_ASTG(stk));
4481 sptr = getcctmp_sc('t', sem.dtemps++, ST_VAR, DTY(dtype), io_sc);
4482 SST_IDP(stk, S_IDENT);
4483 SST_SYMP(stk, sptr);
4484 SST_DTYPEP(stk, DTY(dtype));
4485
4486 (void)mkarg(stk, &dt);
4487 i = SST_ASTG(stk);
4488 PTV(p) = SST_ASTG(stk);
4489
4490 if (A_TYPEG(PTVARREF(p)) == A_ID) {
4491 DOCHK(A_SPTRG(i));
4492 }

4495static void
4496chk_var(SST *stk, int p, int dtype)
4497{
4498 int dt;
4499 int sptr;
4500
4501 if (PTV(p)) /* repeated specifier */
4502 IOERR2(202, PTNAME(p));
4503
4504 if (is_varref(stk)) {
4505 int i;
4506 PT_VARREF(p, 1);
4507 if (DTY(SST_DTYPEG(stk)) != DTY(dtype)) {
4508 if ((DT_ISINT(dtype) && DT_ISINT(SST_DTYPEG(stk))) ||
4509 (DT_ISLOG(dtype) && DT_ISLOG(SST_DTYPEG(stk)))) {
4510 (void)mkarg(stk, &dt);
4511 PT_VARREF(p, SST_ASTG(stk));
4512 sptr = getcctmp_sc('t', sem.dtemps++, ST_VAR, DTY(dtype), io_sc);
4513 SST_IDP(stk, S_IDENT);
4514 SST_SYMP(stk, sptr);
4515 SST_DTYPEP(stk, DTY(dtype));
4516 } else {
4517 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(p));
4518 SST_ASTP(stk, astb.i0);
4519 }
4520 }
4521
4522 (void)mkarg(stk, &dt);
4523 i = SST_ASTG(stk);
4524 PTV(p) = SST_ASTG(stk);
4525
4526 if (A_TYPEG(PTVARREF(p)) == A_ID) {
4527 DOCHK(A_SPTRG(i));
4528 }
4529 } else {
4530 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(p));
4531 SST_ASTP(stk, astb.i0);
4532 }
4533}
4534
4535static void
4536chk_unitid(SST *stk)
4537{
4538 int dtype;
4539 INT unit;
4540
4541 if (PTS(PT_NEWUNIT))
4542 IOERR2(201, "UNIT and NEWUNIT are mutually exclusive");
4543 else if (PTV(PT_UNIT)) /* error if repeated unit specification */
4544 IOERR2(202, "UNIT");
4545
4546 if (stk == NULL) {
4547 /*
4548 * Unit id is the default unit ('*')
4549 */
4550 if (XBIT(124, 0x4)) /* use -5 (stdin) or -6 (stdout) */
4551 unit = -DEFAULT_UNIT;
4552 else /* use 5 or 6 */
4553 unit = DEFAULT_UNIT;
4554 PTV(PT_UNIT) = mk_cval(unit, DT_INT);
4555 } else {
4556 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stk);
4557 if (DT_ISINT(dtype))
4558 /*
4559 * Unit id is an integer expression
4560 */
4561 (void)chktyp(stk, DT_INT, FALSE);
4562 else if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR &&
4563 (SST_IDG(stk) == S_IDENT || SST_IDG(stk) == S_LVALUE)) {
4564 /*
4565 * Unit id specifies an internal file -- a character variable,
4566 * a character array, a character array element, or a character
4567 * substring.
4568 */
4569 (void)mkarg(stk, &dtype);
4570 intern = TRUE;
4571 if (no_rw)
4572 IOERR(211);
4573 else if (!is_read && gbl.currsub && PUREG(gbl.currsub)) {
4574 int sptr;
4575 sptr = sym_of_ast(SST_ASTG(stk));
4576 if (SCG(sptr) == SC_CMBLK)
4577 error(155, 2, gbl.lineno, SYMNAME(gbl.currsub),
4578 "- PURE subprograms may not contain internal WRITE statements "
4579 "where the file unit is a common block variable");
4580 }
4581 } else
4582 IOERR2(201, "UNIT");
4583 PTV(PT_UNIT) = SST_ASTG(stk);
4584 }
4585}
4586
4587static void
4588chk_fmtid(SST *stk)
4589{
4590 int dtype;
4591 int sptr, lab;
4592 ADSC *ad;
4593
4594 fmt_is_var = 0;
4595 if (fmttyp != FT_UNFORMATTED)
4596 IOERR2(202, "FMT");
4597 if (stk == NULL) {
4598 fmttyp = FT_LIST_DIRECTED;
4599 PTV(PT_FMT) = astb.i0;
4600 if (!is_read && unit_star)
4601 print_star = TRUE;
4602 } else {
4603 dtype = SST_DTYPEG(stk);
4604 if (legal_labelvar(dtype)) {
4605 /* If requested, a string is constructed by the scanner
4606 * from the edit list in the FORMAT statement.
4607 */
4608 if (XBIT(58, 0x200))
4609 /* similar check exists in scan.c:get_fmtstr() */
4610 fmttyp = FT_FMTSTR;
4611 else
4612 fmttyp = FT_ENCODED;
4613 if (SST_IDG(stk) == S_CONST) {
4614 /*
4615 * format id is an integer constant representing the statement
4616 * label of a FORMAT statement. First, derive the "name" of the
4617 * label as in the <label> = <integer> reduction.
4618 */
4619 long labno =
4620 DTY(dtype) == TY_INT8 ? CONVAL2G(SST_CVALG(stk)) : SST_CVALG(stk);
4621 lab = declref(getsymf(".L%05ld", labno), ST_LABEL, 'r');
4622 RFCNTI(lab);
4623 /*
4624 * link into list of referenced labels if not already
4625 * there
4626 */
4627 if (SYMLKG(lab) == NOSYM) {
4628 SYMLKP(lab, sem.flabels);
4629 sem.flabels = lab;
4630 }
4631 if (flg.xref)
4632 xrefput(lab, 'r');
4633 sptr = get_fmt_array(lab, ST_PLIST);
4634 REFP(sptr, 1);
4635 PTV(PT_FMT) = mk_id(sptr);
4636 return;
4637 }
4638 if (SST_IDG(stk) == S_IDENT) {
4639 /*
4640 * format id is an integer variable containing a label address
4641 * For 64-byte targets, create a temp variable iff the type
4642 * of the user variable is integer*4.
4643 * When targeting llvm, always create a temp variable of
4644 * ptr-size integer type.
4645 */
4646 (void)mklabelvar(stk);
4647 PTV(PT_FMT) = SST_ASTG(stk);
4648 fmt_is_var = 1;
4649 return;
4650 }
4651 }
4652 /* format id is not a label or integer variable (encoded format case).
4653 * Now, it's either a character string expression (which is the
4654 * standard case) containing a non-encoded format specification.
4655 * Or, a non-standard case is it's a variable, array element, or
4656 * array which contains a hollerith constant containing a non-encoded
4657 * format specification.
4658 */
4659 fmttyp = FT_CHARACTER;
4660 if (DTYG(dtype) == TY_CHAR) { /* standard case */
4661 (void)mkarg(stk, &dtype);
4662 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
4663 fmt_length = astb.i1; /* TBD: need LEN SST_ASTG(stk)) */
4664 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
4665 if (AD_ASSUMSZ(ad) == 0)
4666 fmt_length = AD_NUMELM(ad);
4667 else
4668 IOERR(215);
4669 } else
4670 /*
4671 * mark non-encoded form as a character scalar, constant,
4672 * element, or substring (LET later processing determine
4673 * the length.
4674 */
4675 fmt_length = 0;
4676 } else if (SST_IDG(stk) == S_IDENT || SST_IDG(stk) == S_LVALUE) {
4677 (void)mkarg(stk, &dtype);
4678 fmt_length = astb.i1;
4679 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY) {
4680 switch (A_TYPEG(SST_ASTG(stk))) {
4681 case A_ID:
4682 case A_MEM:
4683 ad = AD_DPTR(dtype);
4684 if (AD_ASSUMSZ(ad) == 0)
4685 fmt_length = AD_NUMELM(ad);
4686 else
4687 IOERR(215);
4688 break;
4689 default:
4690 IOERR2(201, "FMT");
4691 }
4692 }
4693 if (flg.standard)
4694 error(170, 2, gbl.lineno, "nonstandard format specifier", CNULL);
4695 } else
4696 IOERR2(201, "FMT");
4697 PTV(PT_FMT) = SST_ASTG(stk);
4698 }
4699}
4700
4701static void
4702chk_iospec()
4703{
4704 LOGICAL advancingspecified = FALSE;
4705 int adv_ast;
4706
4707 if (!flg.standard)
4708 return;
4709
4710 if (bitv & BITV_ADVANCE) {
4711 adv_ast = PTV(PT_ADVANCE);
4712 if (A_TYPEG(adv_ast) == A_CNST && DTY(A_DTYPEG(adv_ast)) == TY_CHAR &&
4713 (strcmp(stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(A_SPTRG(adv_ast)), "YES") == 0 ||
4714 strcmp(stb.n_base + CONVAL1G(A_SPTRG(adv_ast)), "yes") == 0)) {
4715 advancingspecified = TRUE;
4716 }
4717 }
4718
4719 if (intern && bitv & BITV_ADVANCE) {
4720 IOERR2(201, "internal unit with ADVANCE specifier");
4721 }
4722 if (bitv & BITV_EOR) {
4723 if (!(bitv & BITV_ADVANCE)) {
4724 IOERR2(201, "EOR specified without ADVANCE");
4725 } else if (advancingspecified) {
4726 IOERR2(201, "EOR specified with ADVANCE=YES");
4727 }
4728 }
4729 if (bitv & BITV_SIZE) {
4730 if (!(bitv & BITV_ADVANCE)) {
4731 IOERR2(201, "SIZE specified without ADVANCE");
4732 } else if (advancingspecified) {
4733 IOERR2(201, "SIZE specified with ADVANCE=YES");
4734 }
4735 }
4736}
4737
4738static void
4739put_edit(int code)
4740{
4741 PUT(code);
4742 /*
4743 * If the standard switch is used, save enough state must be saved
4744 * while processing edit descriptors to check for delimiter conformance.
4745 * For this task, the edit processing will be in one of 4 states:
4746 * 0 - initial state: a left paren was just seen.
4747 * 1 - an edit descriptor was just seen, a delimiter or right paren is
4748 * expected.
4749 * 2 - a comma was just seen (this state is entered by the semantic
4750 * actions for "<format item> ::= ,"
4751 * 3 - a colon or slash delimiter was just seen.
4752 * 4 - a edit descriptor DT was just seen ???
4753 */
4754 if (flg.standard) {
4755 switch (edit_state) {
4756 case 0: /* initial state - process edit descriptor after left paren */
4757 switch (code) {
4758 case FED_LPAREN:
4759 break;
4760 case FED_COLON:
4761 case FED_SLASH:
4762 edit_state = 3;
4763 break;
4764 default:
4765 edit_state = 1;
4766 }
4767 break;
4768 case 1: /* an edit descr. was just seen */
4769 switch (code) {
4770 case FED_END:
4771 case FED_RPAREN:
4772 break;
4773 case FED_COLON:
4774 case FED_SLASH:
4775 edit_state = 3;
4776 break;
4777 default:
4778 if (last_edit == FED_P && (code == FED_Fw_d || code == FED_Ew_d ||
4779 code == FED_Dw_d || code == FED_Gw_d))
4780 ;
4781 else if (code == FED_Ee)
4782 ; /* checking has already been done for what Ee can
4783 * follow */
4784 else {
4785 ERR170("missing delimiter in FORMAT");
4786 edit_state = 3;
4787 }
4788 break;
4789 }
4790 break;
4791 case 2: /* a comma was just seen */
4792 if (code == FED_RPAREN)
4793 ERR170("right parenthesis occurred after comma in FORMAT");
4794 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
4795 /*
4796 * fall through for state transition
4797 */
4798 case 3: /* a colon or slash was just seen */
4799 switch (code) {
4800 case FED_LPAREN:
4801 edit_state = 0;
4802 break;
4803 case FED_COLON:
4804 case FED_SLASH:
4805 edit_state = 3;
4806 break;
4807 default:
4808 edit_state = 1;
4809 }
4810 break;
4811 }
4812 switch (code) { /* check for any of the edit extensions */
4813 case FED_Q:
4814 case FED_DOLLAR:
4815 ERR170("using nonstandard edit descriptor");
4816 break;
4817 case FED_Z:
4818 case FED_O:
4819 case FED_L:
4820 case FED_I:
4821 case FED_F:
4822 case FED_E:
4823 case FED_G:
4824 case FED_D:
4825 ERR170("using edit descriptor without specifying width");
4826 break;
4827 }
4828 }
4829 last_edit = code;
4830}
4831
4832static void
4833put_ffield(SST *stk)
4834{
4835 if (SST_IDG(stk) == S_CONST) {
4836 PUT(0);
4837 PUT(SST_CVALG(stk));
4838 } else
4839 interr("put_ffield, not cnst, stkid", SST_IDG(stk), 3);
4840}
4841
4842static void
4843put_vlist(SST *stk)
4844{
4845 int i = 0;
4846 ITEM *iptr;
4847
4848 if (SST_BEGG(stk) == 0) {
4849 interr("put_vlist, vlist is empty", 0, 3);
4850 } else {
4851 for (iptr = SST_BEGG(stk); iptr != ITEM_END; iptr = iptr->next)
4852 i++;
4853
4854 PUT(0);
4855 PUT(i);
4856
4857 /* This field will be used by runtime: RTE_f90io_dts_fmtr/w */
4858 PUT(0);
4859 PUT(0);
4860
4861 for (iptr = SST_BEGG(stk); iptr != ITEM_END; iptr = iptr->next) {
4862 PUT((SST_CVALG(iptr->t.stkp)));
4863 PUT(0);
4864 }
4865 }
4866}

4868static void
4869kwd_errchk(int bt)
4870{
4871 int i;
4872
4873 for (i = 0; i <= PT_MAXV; i++)
4874 if ((PTS(i) && !(PTSTMT(i) & bt)) ||
4875 (bt == BT_INQUIRE && i > 1 && i != PT_ERR && i != PT_END && PTS(i) &&
4876 !PTVARREF(i)))
4877 IOERR2(201, PTNAME(i));
4878}

4880static void
4881_put(INT n, int dtype)
4882{
4883 static const char *desc[] = {
4884 " ", "END", "LP", "RP", "K", "STR",
4885 "T", "TL", "TR", "X", "S", "SP",
4886 "SS", "BN", "BZ", "SLASH", "COLON", "Q",
4887 "DOLLAR", "A", "L", "I", "F", "Ee",
4888 "E", "EN", "ES", "G", "D", "O",
4889 "Z", "AFORMAT", "LFORMAT", "IFORMAT", "OFORMAT", "ZFORMAT",
4890 "FFORMAT", "EFORMAT", "GFORMAT", "DFORMAT", "B", "DT",
4891 "DTFORMAT",
4892 };
4893
4894 if (DBGBIT(3, 128)) {
4895 fprintf(gbl.dbgfil, " %4d: ", fasize);
4896 if (n < 0 && (-n) < (sizeof(desc) / sizeof(char *)))
4897 fprintf(gbl.dbgfil, "%s\n", desc[-n]);
4898 else
4899 fprintf(gbl.dbgfil, "%ld\n", (long)n);
4900 }
4901 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_INT8)
4902 n = cngcon(n, DT_INT4, DT_INT8);
4903 dinit_put(dtype, n);
4904 fasize++;
4905}
